      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I'm parting with my car, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014runs like a dream! It has a few minor signs of love from daily use, but it's totally ready for its next big adventure. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
