    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit utilizes the Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory limited-slip differential. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe to ensure chassis integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping and bushing compliance, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability expected of this platform. A well-sorted driver's car that balances raw performance with mechanical longevity.",
