      "description": "This vehicle is a dependable, well-maintained driver that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and value. Mechanically, it is in excellent shape; the engine pulls strong, the transmission is smooth, and it has been serviced regularly with a full history available. The interior is clean and smoke-free, featuring leather seats that show only light, natural creasing. While the exterior retains a deep gloss, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing consistent with daily use. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that looks great on the road and is ready for its next owner with no immediate work required.",
      "price": 34500.0,
